description: Season two: Two undefeated wrestlers square off on the mat. The Samurai is STRONG, quick, and determined. The Goddess is lithe, lean and skilled. The Samurai starts off quick and uses her strength to her advantage. However, skill and experience soon dominate the match as Isis takes control. Isis goes for the win because she truly enjoys fucking the losers and putting them in their place.
title: The Goddess (2-0) vs. The Samurai (1-0)
